{"tid":1561541,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[踩去西藏]四千公里的單車流浪日記 Live (2) 完","createTime":"2019-09-11T15:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T09:01:14.000Z","uid":241103,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"804e1463834f23c6b64c5d877181414950654d81","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:41:53.000Z","msg":"上文提要<br />\n<br />\n每個人心中都有一份清單，裡面寫嘅都係啲一生人入面好想去做的事。而由香港出發，踩去西藏就其中的一件一人生入面好想去做嘅事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tb2rjuS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftb2rjuS.jpg&h=31d6423c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係2019年6月12日我正式出發，雖然係西藏途遇到啲意外，受過傷，入過院，但而家已經好得七七八八，順利返程，唞多幾日過埋中秋就準備返香港<br />\n<br />\n再次感謝大家一路上嘅支持同鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><del></del><br />\n<br />\n有興趣了解我旅程上嘅經歷嘅巴絲<br />\n可以追舊post<br />\n<br />\n[踩去西藏]四千公里的單車流浪日記 Live<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1246145\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1246145</a><br />\n<br />\n[單車環島]去台灣走轉 順手買地瓜球做手信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1051827\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1051827</a>"},{"pid":"77779f51e50f96b24ff2236dba54549d6dfb43e0","tid":1561541,"uid":5682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qftu6C0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqftu6C0.jpg&h=23ce3992&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvOSjYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcvOSjYn.jpg&h=c1edffca&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FeMP6D2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFeMP6D2.jpg&h=0810fe9c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jmPmXLP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjmPmXLP.png&h=5f6e170e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYO68T8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYO68T8.jpg&h=b22b9f08&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZn4be8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZn4be8.jpg&h=a1744d81&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9nr81V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9nr81V.jpg&h=7475a820&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p55dO38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp55dO38.jpg&h=e72515fd&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"4079e385d573159de92f1a81d2560ba7a3afc63c","tid":1561541,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:43:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"13e3d13e311e3a20354f9f15e21111f5ca0b294d","tid":1561541,"uid":50831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上一個post都未開始追<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83754aa96ad48452e9d05486380e55343f7d495f","tid":1561541,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f0b5e4bd6d70db50c56f71bfc93832b9cc5dfb","tid":1561541,"uid":177727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:12:22.000Z","msg":"支持樓主，隻腳好返未？"},{"pid":"f634285eea8a0f692f4a933aa3eb754bcd85efdd","tid":1561541,"uid":82077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6c52eb2bbb89f6623c39e8f7917de9fe9fa47b","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5f0b5e4bd6d70db50c56f71bfc93832b9cc5dfb","tid":1561541,"uid":177727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:12:22.000Z","msg":"支持樓主，隻腳好返未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:35:24.000Z","msg":"八九成，正常走動冇問題"},{"pid":"1e22764344321755ca48011d883cc81672e48f70","tid":1561541,"uid":53642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:43:02.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ab673eb73f34ad5e1e84859015d25b3e25de122f","tid":1561541,"uid":274319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:07:54.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"7a2ca72d5dbe54d8a1df6d92a184d852a3e9aab5","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:10:42.000Z","msg":"Day 92 印度電影日<br />\n<br />\n今日同尋日差唔多，都係落街下食完早餐就返上樓。晏教依然有訓，唔同嘅係睇咗兩套印度電影 ，大陸釋名叫&lt;小萝莉的猴神大叔&gt;同&lt;印度合伙人&gt;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e47719z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe47719z.jpg&h=c3d341e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NM4aZWc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNM4aZWc.jpg&h=45293e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩套電影都好勵志，兩套劇裡面嘅主角都係做緊一啲人地認為冇可能嘅野，但佢地卻憑著一份信念去堅持呢個目標，最後佢地成功咗<br />\n<br />\n係現實，失敗嘅住住更多，但嘗試，失敗，再嘗試，再失敗，亦係步向成功嘅一個過程。唔知得唔得，但試都唔試就一定唔得<br />\n<br />\n有很多野你唔跟大隊去，唔平平凡凡，想與眾不同既時候，其他人就會覺得你係異類，包括社會，家人同朋友， 甚至排斥你。當你成功咗，當初唔認同你，睇低你嘅人又紛紛祝賀，讚賞你，縱使你依然係以前不合群的一個，真係好諷刺<br />\n<br />\n係而家呢個物質豐盛社會，很多人往往只會睇你揾幾多，有冇車有冇樓，你嘅價值就係睇你搵錢能力，揾到錢就係叻。揾唔到錢，做咩都係晒時間，發白日夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實印度片整體都幾好同有特色， 載歌載舞 唔洗講，其本上都每套都會帶出到啲message令你去思考。不得不提印度國寶級影帝Aamir Khan，佢拍既片其本上都好高質，大家未接觸過印度電影可以先睇佢拍嘅做入門，好似&lt;三個俊瓜&gt;<br />\n<br />\n夜晚表姪女肚餓就陪佢食宵夜，我叫咗碗蟹粥，如果有埋油炸鬼就完美<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PZURKpk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPZURKpk.jpg&h=de12e484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日就中秋，祝大家人月兩圓圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a923dfbf5035271cd7f02204be4e81d9a8a96592","tid":1561541,"uid":82077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:37:28.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日食宵夜有冇肥到"},{"pid":"538d714421bf26775ed06c3109d7f1448785ba56","tid":1561541,"uid":199050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:05:27.000Z","msg":"g持<br />\n香港真係生活逼人，而家更甚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d10347902e45c77061dce8a88a35308a36352a","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a923dfbf5035271cd7f02204be4e81d9a8a96592","tid":1561541,"uid":82077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:37:28.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日食宵夜有冇肥到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:54:08.000Z","msg":"點會冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56db08793508bb6d983600768b51b591a78ddb8","tid":1561541,"uid":265742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:39:29.000Z","msg":"樓主玩公仔機咁勁，不如拍啲教學片上youtube，不過唔知香港受唔受，台灣人就好受<br />\n利申：完全白痴，未中過獎"},{"pid":"d3d5c99def92ed4b69486b8edb7eba35c9074bfc","tid":1561541,"uid":258249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:33:50.000Z","msg":"中秋快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d242db48fc6e1645805131f3fbeab43598fc16a9","tid":1561541,"uid":239291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"追左幾日，終於追到live，中秋節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637f25d8a8e6c75348517dd6264d3ce5ef1657de","tid":1561541,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"樓主中秋快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早日康復<br />\n雖然依家個post變咗大灣區養病日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c999f24852922601b24d667e1f8833e4bef2ffd","tid":1561541,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:55:57.000Z","msg":"樓豬中秋節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0609d07a4c5f7e273d997c2296d52d34a46218","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:21:34.000Z","msg":"中秋節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66351be67b859f0b77f49da82a9e9665fc1c80a","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:05:38.000Z","msg":"Day 93 誅仙<br />\n<br />\n當巴打話齋， 家下變咗養病先頹廢日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於今日有一套電影上映，為咗第一時間睇，我決定聽日再過東莞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yb4a7Lo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyb4a7Lo.jpg&h=421f080e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YaUKsUy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYaUKsUy.jpg&h=c8938070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n揸電動車去戲院嘅時候仲唔小心令手機親吻大地，好彩有Mon貼頂咗一刧<br />\n<br />\n今日首映嘅呢套&lt;誅仙1&gt;係改篇自網絡小説誅仙，有網絡四大名著嘅稱號，係網絡仙俠小説最早期既作品，當年一睇就好似睇金庸咁不能自拔，教都唔訓睇通宵咁濟。佢前中段鋪排得好好，睇得好有味道，可惜個結局就好似趕收工咁，亦因為咁作者比我地一眾書迷屌足咁多年<br />\n<br />\n見到佢出電影真係有啲感慨，好似啲回憶返返晒黎。至於套電影， 大致上都係跟原著，但亦都有唔少改動，如果未睇過原著，整體黎講還可以<br />\n<br />\n相信睇開小說嘅人都明白， 文字先係有最大嘅想像空間，你睇書既時候，書入面嘅人物同影物都大概會有個輪廓同埋畫面。 當你先睇咗書再睇佢改編而成嘅影視作品， 總會有啲格格不入嘅感覺， 因為導演選嘅角可能同你心目中有好大落差<br />\n<br />\n中秋都冇咩點特別做節，係表姐過咗黎一齊食飯。而家過中秋已經冇咗細個嘅感覺，以前細過一到中秋就落街玩燈籠，周圍跑。相反，大個咗就唔想搞咁多野，係屋企好過"},{"pid":"f9f4f18cf384c4ea99bb6771217c5a3899db0ec4","tid":1561541,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:36:11.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c2b298cf336294d22229eff475b2ff79221427af","tid":1561541,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:04:13.000Z","msg":"樓豬都有睇誅仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n碧瑤<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623ffaaa88f4585f2a3475ab69cd26d693c3c9bf","tid":1561541,"uid":245791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T20:23:15.000Z","msg":"追到Live 留一留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d1872077caee9959459f7311a8536f5ad35dcb","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2b298cf336294d22229eff475b2ff79221427af","tid":1561541,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:04:13.000Z","msg":"樓豬都有睇誅仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n碧瑤<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n碧瑤<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n田不易<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5f5dc6fb5e253424a430c565e5c7a4010a6902","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:39:54.000Z","msg":"中秋翌日，暫停更新一日，聽日補發<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4ed0ad35c6e360b6b2845d7d81d5e01837364d","tid":1561541,"uid":119774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:38:44.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c912faed651be1d904813b92ba2fb3ab357434","tid":1561541,"uid":52162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc50413c8d1cb08f32b4387ced11599eaf477c2","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:28:06.000Z","msg":"Day 95 東莞大朗<br />\n<br />\n本來係尋日過大朗的，但姑丈叫我留多日，所以我今日先過。尋日無咩特別就唔講了<br />\n<br />\n今日食完午餐，睇咗陣電視就坐公交車去客運站，去到啱啱二點。排陣買車飛啦，吖，得返五點嘅加班車，我個心當堂屌咗聲。於是我冇買住，嘗試揾下有冇啲再快捷啲嘅，但睇咗火車， call車等各種方法，衡量咗一下，都係死死地氣買五點嘅車飛算<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/16/005714_06245f86deaab149c3aed992a6f9fc79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F16%2F005714_06245f86deaab149c3aed992a6f9fc79.jpg&h=72261570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拎住一袋二袋，我直接入候車區等算。對上嘅班次分別係1510同1610，兩次檢票都去咗碰運氣，睇下有冇人冇上，有位可以補上，唔洗等到五點，可惜事與願違<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/16/010432_de3f6b0839651876169e78289b6cc9ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F16%2F010432_de3f6b0839651876169e78289b6cc9ba.jpg&h=a62abece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐上去大朗嘅車，兩個半鐘車程，旁邊不是女的，沒聊天的動力，唯有睇書黎消磨一下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/16/011021_0757c70f7ff9f91fe8ad80e60f4ecb0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F16%2F011021_0757c70f7ff9f91fe8ad80e60f4ecb0e.jpg&h=8a31d7ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hrANGLQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhrANGLQ.jpg&h=c2263aec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到天已黑，舅父舅母同表嫂黎咗接我，之後去咗茶記食飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2oScST7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2oScST7.jpg&h=46c3343a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返到去就見到成個廳都係表姨甥仔啲玩具，呢件要配合兒童電批，可以肢解隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6YqYOtS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6YqYOtS.jpg&h=2dfe92a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前細過返黎就訓廳，後來表姐嫁咗，就訓佢間房，而家變咗表姨甥女嘅房，我嘅到來就係霸佔佢間可愛公主風嘅房，不過佢平時鐘意痴住佢媽訓，影響不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T88zmRZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT88zmRZ.jpg&h=84908daf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日有時間可以砌返部車，十分期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b80e5f6b29882300d2dbe0916f4c8fd491b3a6c","tid":1561541,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:41:57.000Z","msg":"巴打會唔會砌返架車，由大朗踩返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5304ffc4269f6f3a7d8668b6bc0a9ac47f5f5a","tid":1561541,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:46:47.000Z","msg":"幾個月冇追甩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df18bd6d25692d3ae4d9200375aa8faebbd7e660","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b80e5f6b29882300d2dbe0916f4c8fd491b3a6c","tid":1561541,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:41:57.000Z","msg":"巴打會唔會砌返架車，由大朗踩返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"唔會，隻腳未好晒，再踩段長途應該會傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce75ab21cfa748c4360de0a9fe28a96760d84a16","tid":1561541,"uid":34099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:08:30.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"fc43d5df2c1296c1ca2f61baf1f72870e2080549","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:09:09.000Z","msg":"Day 96 大朗日常一<br />\n<br />\n今朝起身全屋人都出晒門，我食咗包雞胸，落飯廳拎咗支旺仔牛奶飲，見到有個流沙包，順便食埋，之後上返房玩手機<br />\n<br />\n表哥入院幾日做body check，午飯時間表嫂去醫院探表哥，我跟埋去。冇見一排，佢瘦咗好多， 佢都話差啲唔認得我，而家個造型十足十韓國電影&lt;犯罪都市&gt;入面嘅反派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係醫院飯堂買飯，拎上房食。我發現呢度啲護士後生既都幾多，而且唔少靚女。表哥仲同我講邊個性格開朗啲，邊個唔太出聲，如果我覺得啱心水聊人傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNuOy63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNuOy63.jpg&h=0dbd5b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uu6hsr8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuu6hsr8.jpg&h=18a9dffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CURM5dU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCURM5dU.jpg&h=23cc169d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n探完表哥就返屋企，表哥怕我係屋企悶，叫我去佢個朋友間健身工作室玩。真的太好，有成三個月冇做gym，終於可以過手癮， 嚟緊呢幾日嘅下午都唔使無所事事了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wogpRXk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwogpRXk.jpg&h=a89d7cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做完gym，表嫂就過嚟車我去食飯， 食紙包魚嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDFuiD3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDFuiD3.jpg&h=ccbde434&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4353157086782f582a175d0b5149b828cd8a66f","tid":1561541,"uid":213945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:01:02.000Z","msg":"輸出革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cba71005be753eea23fc0c352cf2b4558470984","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:25:34.000Z","msg":"Day 97 大朗日常二<br />\n<br />\n今朝起身揸咗架表哥架電動車去街口食早餐，王師傅腸粉，叫咗豬潤蛋腸，味道幾好，但順德嗰檔好食啲同平啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yAtvUPf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyAtvUPf.jpg&h=7bac378e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後返屋企睇電視，等食晏，食完落咗地下砌車，身水身汗。搞咗一輪先砌返靚仔，但前輪碟片有啲彎咗，要揾架餐搞搞佢，睇下調唔調得返，可惜唔知的鉗放邊，佢地又出晒門，唯有聽日再處理。而且想帶部車去沖下涼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vmVREjc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvmVREjc.jpg&h=12e20d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次砌車都對架車既各方面更熟悉啲，其本上都舞得掂，各種小問題自己都處理到。不過架車經過今次西藏之旅，都有返咁上吓磨損度，有唔少疤痕，算得上係架有經歷嘅車<br />\n<br />\n舅母冇煮飯，今晚嘅晚餐得豆腐花同油糍，再加出前一丁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dubYjnr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdubYjnr.jpg&h=1c9f3229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g0d0xHF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg0d0xHF.jpg&h=d7cfcf6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完唞咗陣就揸電動車去Gay room。夜晚都幾多後生女做gym。做完gym返歸食咗包雞胸同盒奶做宵夜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V8ZV53g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV8ZV53g.jpg&h=d202b372&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VwzySJP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVwzySJP.jpg&h=4a5b0cd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16167f0075e8abec734b57144d933bd9a892d65d","tid":1561541,"uid":76208,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:55:47.000Z","msg":"唔知點解會繼續想追樓主既養生日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb67ec380649d56ba10dbfb3a81fe87b48d3697","tid":1561541,"uid":9170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T00:42:02.000Z","msg":"樓主幾時返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48588b9001259528ccb2f48432cba64050d01097","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bb67ec380649d56ba10dbfb3a81fe87b48d3697","tid":1561541,"uid":9170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T00:42:02.000Z","msg":"樓主幾時返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:29:21.000Z","msg":"下星期一"},{"pid":"b0f6621842d7304af479a7b1a4dd625fe3fdde4a","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16167f0075e8abec734b57144d933bd9a892d65d","tid":1561541,"uid":76208,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:55:47.000Z","msg":"唔知點解會繼續想追樓主既養生日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有人話連續七日做同樣嘅野就會變成習慣"},{"pid":"ecde927c2532dda4e7f05ed25904a94617f29274","tid":1561541,"uid":54805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:30:40.000Z","msg":"樓主番到香港都update 下近況呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3228ff10a4175c682553818f12d332212632ef34","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:02:12.000Z","msg":"Day 97 大朗日常三<br />\n<br />\n今晚都係揸電動車去食腸粉，一條八蚊冬菇蛋，一條六蚊淨蛋，加咗支維他奶，同對面枱嘅伯父對視咗眼，繼續悠然自得嘆我個早餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVgtPKb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVgtPKb.jpg&h=eb1dad11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於舅母去咗貴州旅行，禮拜先返，今日晏就由舅父煮，煎蛋加麵，一餐半餐將就下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下午汁咗汁架車同駄包，汁咗陣就想訓教，訓教已成習慣，訓醒食晚飯。都係舅父煮，三餸冇湯，比下午豐富好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a3CpocR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa3CpocR.jpg&h=15017ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8BqBYMh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8BqBYMh.jpg&h=48f955d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚嘅街道，由舅父屋企出發，揸十幾分鐘就到gym room。不過有段路整路，路面情況唔太好，凹凸不平，加上部電動車嘅避震極差，連過 坑渠蓋都feel到有明顯震動，更何況係爛路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tcam9VB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcam9VB.jpg&h=0e81e908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚黎真係多女啲，不過我係黎鍛鍊的，有靚女只係bonus。加油啊，你嘅努力係唔會白費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cArEWBs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcArEWBs.jpg&h=2304dc01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返到屋企見表姨甥女喺度磅重同埋測體脂， 我有磅埋一份。 經過一輪嘅休養體重又上升返，變番原本嘅70kg， 他一個方面都正正常常不過不失<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JNKCJhY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJNKCJhY.jpg&h=ab4a3481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中間有段幾搞笑嘅插曲， 我表姨甥女聽日問邊個車佢返學(平時係舅母車嘅)， 表嫂就話爸爸聽日車你， 跟住我見到表姨甥女整咗個面容扭曲怪表情出嚟話唔制。 我就問佢爸爸車你唔好咩， 佢答我因為爸爸車佢返學會遲到。再問有幾大機率， 佢話係每次都會。表哥真好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n表姨甥仔嘅玩具都幾多， 呢把槍令我諗返起以前細個睇電視廣告成日好想買玩具反斗城嗰把 射發泡膠嘅衝鋒槍。 到時可以買咗比佢做生日禮物，順便自己過下癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvJjWD1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvJjWD1.jpg&h=5c3ea930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JGzfu4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGzfu4t.jpg&h=3b757bc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網睇咗睇，啲款多到呢，一百連發，好撚爽咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQ9y1bY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQ9y1bY.jpg&h=40607bc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa48a928e5a34510e6d95cee2bac3b49d214e83a","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:02:59.000Z","msg":"打錯，Day 98先啱"},{"pid":"725579bdc5ff07c2fbf44d909e47ddc376c0b4fe","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecde927c2532dda4e7f05ed25904a94617f29274","tid":1561541,"uid":54805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:30:40.000Z","msg":"樓主番到香港都update 下近況呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:05:27.000Z","msg":"睇情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba218b9264213b5285ea2b5381d4aae82f6a66d","tid":1561541,"uid":265742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:48:59.000Z","msg":"養生日子都幾好睇，返到香港都keep住間中update下"},{"pid":"75b56bfe55730e244337d6068cbd277316baa8a1","tid":1561541,"uid":214670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:28:02.000Z","msg":"樓主有咁多親戚真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12cb8da2f1f16626a4e93643532ca327237026c4","tid":1561541,"uid":196329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"725579bdc5ff07c2fbf44d909e47ddc376c0b4fe","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecde927c2532dda4e7f05ed25904a94617f29274","tid":1561541,"uid":54805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:30:40.000Z","msg":"樓主番到香港都update 下近況呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:05:27.000Z","msg":"睇情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T12:27:15.000Z","msg":"想繼續睇返到香港養傷日記，9hea日記<br />\n什麼搵工日記，返工日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cea43ea0fb37a6ff7238ebd7a5561eb46f8330","tid":1561541,"uid":54805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12cb8da2f1f16626a4e93643532ca327237026c4","tid":1561541,"uid":196329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"725579bdc5ff07c2fbf44d909e47ddc376c0b4fe","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecde927c2532dda4e7f05ed25904a94617f29274","tid":1561541,"uid":54805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:30:40.000Z","msg":"樓主番到香港都update 下近況呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:05:27.000Z","msg":"睇情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T12:27:15.000Z","msg":"想繼續睇返到香港養傷日記，9hea日記<br />\n什麼搵工日記，返工日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T15:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a5b6d9a8fda6db17d9e2260666c2fcf32bfedd","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T15:41:00.000Z","msg":"Day 98 大朗日常四<br />\n<br />\n朝早例牌食腸粉加支維他奶，埋單11蚊，上午都係9hea，玩下手機睇下江蘇衛視朝早重播嘅非誠勿擾，等食晏。點知舅父又煮麵，煮麵唔係問題，問題係嗰款麵口感好差，完全冇彈性<br />\n<br />\n表哥話我未坐過東莞呢邊嘅城軌，下午帶我坐出東筦，再轉地鐵過厚街萬達廣場行街。城軌站少人到一個點，班次半個鐘一班，地鐵就正常人流<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zy62hrx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZy62hrx.jpg&h=75219779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2aFOym.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2aFOym.jpg&h=02d41a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3sgd8yx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3sgd8yx.jpg&h=616198a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到厚街萬達，行咗個圈，冇咩特別，表哥買咗條褲。地下有個展場，啲古裝照公司做推廣。有啲model換晒古裝坐出黎比大家影相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vib5ZGX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVib5ZGX.jpg&h=0c4361b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R89vrng.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR89vrng.jpg&h=ed85b7be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我之前貪過癮，同埋嗰fd都去影過，扮電影&lt;繡春刀&gt;嘅錦衣衛。個化妝師可能幫慣囡囡化，比佢化完當堂有少少妖氣，十足十林平之練完避邪劍法嘅感覺，最後影出黎我以為自己神功大成，IG都唔敢post，驚係黑木崖比人圍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnAnhyJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnAnhyJ.jpg&h=dd61f7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我份人都幾鐘意扮鬼扮馬，聖誕節著充氣鹿衫去尖咀扮聖誕老人，哈佬喂孭個發泡膠棺材去海洋公園，去東京著武士盔甲扮真田幸村，係故宮門口著啲on9劇服我扮大臣fd扮皇帝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aouZ4ip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaouZ4ip.jpg&h=769f2285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n揾咗嗰同我一齊癲嘅fd打算動漫節去cosplay玩下，反正未試過，但未諗到扮邊個，大家可以比啲建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下午茶食食咗份煎餅果子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fzz7tMJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffzz7tMJ.jpg&h=06044278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fua216O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFua216O.jpg&h=a24895ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚餐去咗間航空主題餐廳据扒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCGRa0M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCGRa0M.jpg&h=50b9bf43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFFeTeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFFeTeb.jpg&h=1140bab1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b29Wm7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb29Wm7A.jpg&h=0c5383a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mqxdpk0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMqxdpk0.jpg&h=ab664d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5PLB6zp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5PLB6zp.jpg&h=643cd98b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66ec4230e24bdfdf465f852df3c529e7955a4407","tid":1561541,"uid":82077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"日日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似都唔重既"},{"pid":"901413839fde47d258b3562174d032eed26d42e3","tid":1561541,"uid":48761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017d46b4a4fdb02b57173359687d32f4cbfd6aaf","tid":1561541,"uid":150561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d8fc68e397c1639d14efb9133e233ec6a8241c","tid":1561541,"uid":54805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:29:46.000Z","msg":"人呢"},{"pid":"639a3d601b6a53c439e70faefd9635ae45b66887","tid":1561541,"uid":260202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:10:11.000Z","msg":"巴打返左香港未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96be4cd5d42d5f0edeccbe7b8ed1ffd033c15fba","tid":1561541,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:32:10.000Z","msg":"人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869a99b11fc8a8b54ac066b4e1a9b9d8cbf01470","tid":1561541,"uid":214670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T22:13:17.000Z","msg":"巴打消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85febec6ced5500d7ffa238c80a1ecb87aaad317","tid":1561541,"uid":9170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:18:45.000Z","msg":"巴打好似話星期一返香港"},{"pid":"0857b401832f272ba2233e387de594ef4e2279fd","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:28:19.000Z","msg":"冇被消失 潛咗幾晚水 今晚出post <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身係尋日返香港，但阿媽叫我係鄉下玩多幾日都唔緊，最好過埋十一先出，但我真係頂唔緊，想返黎找下工，claim埋啲保險，找埋啲人情債，所以留多咗兩日，聽日先返香港<br />\n<br />\n如果聽晚冇出post就可能係過關被人扣咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13f6895d7a8f3dcecabd01d80fecf0c6a7d5007","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:04:41.000Z","msg":"Day 102 潛水的日子<br />\n<br />\n潛咗水幾日，今日終於浦頭，呢幾日主要都係見下親戚，同出去食飯咁。其餘時間真係廢人咁，長期攤係床，連手機都唔想玩，醉生夢死，真正嘅虛渡光陰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvXQ4CK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrvXQ4CK.jpg&h=35198d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dE7Q4CR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdE7Q4CR.jpg&h=28e8a206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中一朝早就同咗我大姨同姨丈出去飲茶。兩個都退咗休，平時都係收下租，飲茶散步過日晨，本來日子好清閒，可惜我另外個表哥不務正業，成日去蒲同賭，散咗佢地唔少錢，希望佢浪子回頭，不過機會真係唔大，除非有啲好深刻嘅教訓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WiT489h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWiT489h.jpg&h=c3685395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大前晚就同咗表姐表姐夫一齊去松山湖嘅一間酒店食自助餐，啲生蠔幾高質，食咗一打<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3rit9N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3rit9N.jpg&h=b8fe105d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KoK76WE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKoK76WE.jpg&h=20bf2887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjYg0gU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjYg0gU.jpg&h=01246977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前晚表哥車咗我去另一個表姐新屋度坐，成棟一共十層，頂樓三千呎自住，其餘全部放租。望見嗰陽台都已經大過自己香港間屋，就覺得香港幾百萬先得幾百呎仲要供成世為咩，寧願拎啲錢去外國又好國内又好，係啲小鎮過下日子算。但自己一個就話姐，要成家立室，又唔同講法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pB1qTFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpB1qTFQ.jpg&h=56db7bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲表哥表姐大部分都80後，佢地之間嘅話題都離不開仔女，工作，起樓收租同健康狀況。對我黎講呢啲野相信好快會發生，除咗買地起樓。睇住大家都過得唔錯，而自己係最無成就嘅一個，心裡面難免有啲唔好受<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzpDvDw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzpDvDw.jpg&h=725585cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇對比就冇傷害<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時夜晚行閒冇野做，就去健身室做gym room做下gym，昅下女。有時就去松山湖邊嘅人行徑散下步<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ENDMEzR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENDMEzR.jpg&h=f36b192c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p1b2Xnj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp1b2Xnj.jpg&h=ae181384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高空停車場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVQrEDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVQrEDb.jpg&h=cf08764a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為廠房啲民工放工<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vz0J2z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7vz0J2z.jpg&h=d36c2919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋晚臨訓前係房玩手機，聽到出面街有爭執聲，於是出咗陽台睇。見到有一男一女係馬路中間互相打鬥。我食咗冇陣花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X7iHXpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX7iHXpG.jpg&h=9baeeaaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日起身前發咗個夢，夢見自己返香港比綠色物體警犬圍，我奪命狂奔先突破重圍，但返到屋企樓下有重兵注防，要智取先入到大堂，一搭life就醒咗，有啲膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚表哥帶咗我去另一個親戚到坐，喝下茶。我從佢地嘅對話當中接觸到炒茶呢樣野，唔係茶是故鄉濃嗰啲擇茶葉炒，係炒樓嗰種炒。佢地係買一箱箱茶餅返黎等升值，幾年前七千蚊一箱嘅而家升到四十二萬係咩概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56368ab72f935b51c58cd4a5763d2f8689487ab3","tid":1561541,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0857b401832f272ba2233e387de594ef4e2279fd","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:28:19.000Z","msg":"冇被消失 潛咗幾晚水 今晚出post <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身係尋日返香港，但阿媽叫我係鄉下玩多幾日都唔緊，最好過埋十一先出，但我真係頂唔緊，想返黎找下工，claim埋啲保險，找埋啲人情債，所以留多咗兩日，聽日先返香港<br />\n<br />\n如果聽晚冇出post就可能係過關被人扣咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"巴打，唔好著黑衫過關<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a176b62b990c06f77648cb49aa12361e0864d5a","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:00:41.000Z","msg":"咩都冇查，順利回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009876f9c65073112c1abd85c145cc76291a64ed","tid":1561541,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"表可姊咁撚有$<br />\n又靠收地發達？<br />\n每月收租有冇十皮，點解仲做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9714dfb45d4391434de95a64822f3f470f05f517","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"009876f9c65073112c1abd85c145cc76291a64ed","tid":1561541,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"表可姊咁撚有$<br />\n又靠收地發達？<br />\n每月收租有冇十皮，點解仲做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:54:09.000Z","msg":"收地致富<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知收幾多，淨係知其中一棟收緊八十萬租一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然收租的確唔洗做，但佢地入村委啊，政府做野係想上到位，有埋權勢，咁就可以再揾更多嘅錢，成就人生巔峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a919e220f9289284da62e7691f2108c8b806f74","tid":1561541,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9714dfb45d4391434de95a64822f3f470f05f517","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"009876f9c65073112c1abd85c145cc76291a64ed","tid":1561541,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"表可姊咁撚有$<br />\n又靠收地發達？<br />\n每月收租有冇十皮，點解仲做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:54:09.000Z","msg":"收地致富<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知收幾多，淨係知其中一棟收緊八十萬租一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然收租的確唔洗做，但佢地入村委啊，政府做野係想上到位，有埋權勢，咁就可以再揾更多嘅錢，成就人生巔峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234aae6a4574a56e86c7bd3fbdcde5135e2c2fdf","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:13:55.000Z","msg":"Day 103 回家<br />\n<br />\n不經不覺已經出走咗三個月，時間真係過得好快，所有野就好似前兩日發生咁<br />\n<br />\n朝早食埋返香港前最後一餐腸粉，就上返房汁行李。午餐就過咗對面間湘菜館食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZQzcuF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZQzcuF.jpg&h=082a21f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完表哥就車我去坐車，去到二點三，坐搭九嘅嗰班。如果冇塞車，坐大約一個鐘到就到羅湖口岸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c02avhs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc02avhs.jpg&h=f5005276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OLshUKa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOLshUKa.jpg&h=c3dc8b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o9CUWXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9CUWXD.jpg&h=7e9aceee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iUh9LQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiUh9LQ4.jpg&h=fec1c020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到咗羅湖，過關冇咩特別，只係拉行李都要過機，唔似以前抽樣。亦都冇查手機，問話，拍祝賀片段呢啲事發生。好順利咁坐上地鐵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HhJpzLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHhJpzLM.jpg&h=3c8d6b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重返久違嘅屋企， 有種嘅陌生又熟悉嘅感覺，除咗細間都係好細間，有啲壓迫感咁。阿媽煮嘅飯，嗰種味道始終係第到係食唔到嘅，一切又開始回到原來嘅軌道上。食完飯，我拎返封塵好耐嘅茶壺沖咗壺大紅袍，品嚐路上嘅種種經歷<br />\n<br />\n回想返一路走過嘅，當時嘅辛苦已經遺忘了，記起嘅都係段段難忘嘅經歷，酒店嘅靈異，貴州嘅爛路，摸黑落山嘅驚險，路上認識嘅朋友，折多山上嘅高反，抄車坐白車住院嘅無奈，到拉薩嘅激動，望到珠峰嘅無憾，仲有最後休養嘅日子。呢種種經歷都仿如昨天，相信無論隔幾耐，只要回想返呢段旅程，我都會會心一笑<br />\n<br />\n世界哪麼大，我想去看看<br />\n<br />\n在呢個世界，每個人都想盡可能用自己想嘅方式嘅活著，有人選擇安穩，有人選擇冒險，無論行咩路，都係一種歷練，無話誰對誰錯。都係嗰句啦條路自己揀，前面係懸崖都唔好怨天尤人， 話唔定跌落去會有奇遇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ohqbZy0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FohqbZy0.jpg&h=1bab5424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四千公里嘅單車流浪之旅正式完結，呢個post可能間唔中更新下，大家有咩想問都可以繼續留言。希望係不久嘅將來可以再出新post，分享下一段旅程。再一次衷心感謝大家一路以黎嘅支持同鼓勵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mDEgrb3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmDEgrb3.gif&h=203bda9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e8e41373fdb957e52cd895605440a49476615ed","tid":1561541,"uid":16697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3cf029d2b112183c28dc96757034eb5714df1c","tid":1561541,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:27:44.000Z","msg":"返到香港，第一餐食乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab881ceaa8ae7cf626e6051e71ef27d2d1d47a74","tid":1561541,"uid":214670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T23:49:53.000Z","msg":"上次過完中秋番落黎，過關時我未拎番張回鄉証就已經有個男海關準備攔抵我，之後要比回鄉証佢去第二部機再查多次，又問我背囊裝咩，不過可能我過關果陣已經夜晚十一點幾就收工，所以問完就放我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e22ad9ce679dbe192cd12ae2621b8a773bb1ccb","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e8e41373fdb957e52cd895605440a49476615ed","tid":1561541,"uid":16697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ff6d793cfa88f169b50bc309bfe8d1c52f7526","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a3cf029d2b112183c28dc96757034eb5714df1c","tid":1561541,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:27:44.000Z","msg":"返到香港，第一餐食乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"打算去三哥食兩份雞肉竹笙小辣，加份皮蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e844699dbb794edcacd0b945c9c54e39e7d0d97","tid":1561541,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05ff6d793cfa88f169b50bc309bfe8d1c52f7526","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a3cf029d2b112183c28dc96757034eb5714df1c","tid":1561541,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:27:44.000Z","msg":"返到香港，第一餐食乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"打算去三哥食兩份雞肉竹笙小辣，加份皮蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:10:46.000Z","msg":"大辣無難度吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df772aaaa0e780e92e54ebd86efe81edc4932d9b","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e844699dbb794edcacd0b945c9c54e39e7d0d97","tid":1561541,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05ff6d793cfa88f169b50bc309bfe8d1c52f7526","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a3cf029d2b112183c28dc96757034eb5714df1c","tid":1561541,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:27:44.000Z","msg":"返到香港，第一餐食乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"打算去三哥食兩份雞肉竹笙小辣，加份皮蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:10:46.000Z","msg":"大辣無難度吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:12:31.000Z","msg":"冇，但唔想爆汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fc25bea08884e9ea6204facfb5be4e2d123536","tid":1561541,"uid":172329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f01ff89733f574f026620e3ae5ff97141cc667e","tid":1561541,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9fc25bea08884e9ea6204facfb5be4e2d123536","tid":1561541,"uid":172329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4be761bb571dcb31a327c2f30e3c9c9d88212f6","tid":1561541,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"樓豬點"}]}